               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t16870114-3-off13-c31" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-3-defend36 t16870114-3-off13 t16870114-3-verdict15"></join>
         
               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t16870114-3-defend36" type="defendantName">
                     Richard 
                     Roberts
                  <interp inst="t16870114-3-defend36" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-defend36" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-defend36" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , of the Parish of <placeName id="t16870114-3-defloc12">St. Dunstans in the West</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16870114-3-defloc12" type="placeName" value="St. Dunstans in the West"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16870114-3-defloc12" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-3-defend36 t16870114-3-defloc12"></join>, was Indicted for <rs id="t16870114-3-off13" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-off13" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-off13" type="offenceSubcategory" value="robbery"></interp>
               stealing one Sword with a silver Hilt, value 59 s. one Watch with a Gold Case, value 12 l. two Stone Seals, value 40 s. on the <rs id="t16870114-3-cd14" type="crimeDate">25th. of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-3-off13 t16870114-3-cd14"></join> last, the Goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t16870114-3-victim38" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Elvin
                        <interp inst="t16870114-3-victim38" type="surname" value="Elvin"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16870114-3-victim38" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16870114-3-victim38" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-3-off13 t16870114-3-victim38"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  . The Evidence against the Prisoner deposed, that as the Prosecutor was Rideing along the Street, the Prisoner came behind him, and suddenly snatch'd away his Sword from his side
            </rs>, but he could not charge the other Goods upon the Prisoner, yet the Prisoner having but little to say for himself, he was found <rs id="t16870114-3-verdict15" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-verdict15" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t16870114-3-punish16" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16870114-3-punish16" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t16870114-3-defend36 t16870114-3-punish16"></join>
               
                     <note>[Death. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
